</div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good afternoon Rafa=
ella,</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;=
,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I wanted to take th=
e time to thank you very much for meeting with Chris, David and myself at y=
our place this afternoon. It was much appreciated.</span><span style=3D"fon=
t-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span=
></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I felt that the mee=
ting was very productive and positive as we all discussed the next steps an=
d have agreed on the claim=E2=80=99s progression process moving forward.</s=
pan><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-se=
rif"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I would like to re-=
confirm the next steps we agreed to in writing, and share with all as below=
:</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,san=
s-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><span =
style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>=
</o:p></span></p>
</div>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0in" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;ms=
o-list:l0 level1 lfo2">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Asset Restore to attend site as soon as po=
ssible and complete the process of assessing and cataloging the contents fo=
r the response of the contents claim. After assessment the contents which a=
re categorised as a total loss will
 be removed from site.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&q=
uot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListPa=
ragraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Asset Restore to strip out the property of=
 any fire or smoke damaged linings or other non-structural items. This will=
 enable a clear and clean structural assessment to be undertaken, from whic=
h we will produce a scope of works
 for the repairs required.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-famil=
y:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoLi=
stParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 l=
fo2">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Once we have a scope of works completed =
